snippet.title: Amber Heard Responds to Johnny Depp's $7 Million Claim | Flixet
snippet.description:
In today’s video, we gonna tell you about Amber Heard’s response to Johnny Depp's claim of not donating $7 million. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
____________________________________________

Amber Heard's attorney released a statement in response to Johnny Depp's legal team's claim that the actress didn't donate the $7 million she received as part of their divorce settlement. 

Music In This Video : 

Track: Odessa — LiQWYD & Scandinavianz

Watch: https://youtu.be/jNy-Dp3lgcg
